  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  DEFINE VARIABLE cMessage AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
  DEFINE VARIABLE lSuccess AS LOGICAL NO-UNDO.
